 get
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#get">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>使用 @ 指定版本&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>代码规范</title><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Golang/%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Oct 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Golang/%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="语言规范">
 语言规范
